HEADWORD: Discurrent
<hw>Dis*cur"rent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not current or
free to circulate; not in use.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Sir E.
Sandys.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
